{"tid":2117002,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"經常上連登的好與壞","createTime":"2020-07-20T13:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T15:02:50.000Z","uid":339980,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b806d92548764a3a73ba81dfd6e8d3a7c45049","tid":2117002,"uid":339980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始<br />\n平均每日用最少有2、3個鐘頭上連登<br />\n<br />\n連登係資訊豐富嘅平台<br />\n平時得閒，第一樣諗到嘅就係上連登<br />\n唔知算唔算中左「連登癮」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時候會諗...<br />\n如果我唔上連登<br />\n將呢啲時間投放喺其他地方<br />\n我嘅生活會唔會更加多姿多彩呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲試過戒連登？有咩改變？<br />\n又或者講吓連登帶俾你啲咩好與壞<br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n好：<br />\n- 啟發思考，連登仔嘅思維方式非常獨到<br />\n<br />\n壞：<br />\n- 浪費左好多時間去睇野，少左時間做野"},{"pid":"78defc050260d3f9b361b61b972eb2368bf42be7","tid":2117002,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"我每日用上10個鐘up吸收連登資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308ec75ab45d4346434b91bdeeda8ec1ae876157","tid":2117002,"uid":58880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"每日除左打丁就係上連登成人台"},{"pid":"f15fc6f5f8efdc96fc3e3576f03151220ef50f87","tid":2117002,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"308ec75ab45d4346434b91bdeeda8ec1ae876157","tid":2117002,"uid":58880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"每日除左打丁就係上連登成人台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:56:46.000Z",